<%# Customizability %>
<section class="hero" id="about">
  <div class="hero-body">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="title is-size-2">It's all customizable.</p>
      <p class="subtitle is-size-4"><%= bot.user.username %> is designed to be heavily tweaked and customized.</p>
      <p><%= bot.user.username %> is designed with a KISS principle - but it's also extremely hackable.</p>
      <p>Nearly every major feature or module is configurable, so you can fit things to fit any server.</p>
      <p>You can even set thresholds for the automod system and opt-out of individual logger events.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

